#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Kolf is a miniature golf game. The game is played from an overhead view, "
#| "with a hort bar representing the golf club. Kolf features many different "
#| "types of objects, such water hazards, slopes, sand traps, and black holes "
#| "(warps), among others."
msgid ""
"Kolf is a miniature golf game. The game is played from an overhead view, "
"with a short bar representing the golf club. Kolf features many different "
"types of objects, such water hazards, slopes, sand traps, and black holes "
"(warps), among others."
msgstr ""
"Kgolf adalah permainan golf miniatur. Permainan dimainkan dari sebuah "
"tampilan permukaan tanah, dengan hort bar mewakili klub golf. Fitur Kolf "
"banyak tipe objek yang berbeda, seperti bahaya air, lereng, perangkap pasir, "
"dan lubang hitam (lengkungan), dan yang lainnya."

